channel.title: Whenever i try to run my server
channel.description: when i try run it from my source, i get a error occurred during initialization of UM, anyone know a fix??

item.title: Whenever i try to run my server
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

  1. Are you running it through eclipse?
  2. What architecture is your computer (32- | 64-bit)? You can find this out by doing Right-click > My Computer > Properties, and then looking at the “System type:”
  3. What version of Java are you running? Do you have both the JDK and JRE? If so what versions, and what architecture (Control Panel > Programs, then look for the Java ones)

no jew silly g00sse. He mens the jaba universal machine.[/quote]

Not sure if you’re using sarcasm… It’s VM; Virtual Machine.

The run.bat is coded wrong. Post your run.bat, please.
